name: Elemental Door
description:
How many keys are needed to open this door? 🗝

Here is your key, I give it to you. Take the reins of your life, there is no narrow or wide path, irregular or flat, there is your path, you do it.
You are the way, you are the key and you are the door, you are also the mystery on the other side of the door.
